@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Default search request (no body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/milestones/search

### Filtered search request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/milestones/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"filters": {
		"state": "all",
		"titleSearch": "release",
		"milestoneIds": [1, 2, 3]
	}
}

### Invalid search request (unsupported state)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/milestones/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"filters": {
		"state": "opened"
	}
}

### Invalid search request (duplicate milestoneIds)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/milestones/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"filters": {
		"milestoneIds": [3, 3]
	}
}
